cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

This paper deals with computer vision tasks such as frame interpolation and optical flow estimation using CNNs. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses unsupervised learning and proxy tasks, which are related to machine learning and artificial intelligence, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely categories as well. The use of real movies and CNNs also suggests that the paper may fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.RO (Robotics) categories, respectively.
